{"type":"message","id":"88a1a1f0","parentId":"92a7dddc","timestamp":"2026-03-22T12:37:08.949Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我当前使用的插件列表中 **没有** 专门的记忆增强插件。已有的插件主要是 Feishu（飞书）相关功能、微信、以及 OpenClaw‑WeChat 等渠道插件。如果你想要启用记忆增强，需要另外安装相应的插件（如 `memory‑lancedb‑pro` 或 `openviking`），然后重启网关使其生效。需要我帮你安装其中的一个吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":16762,"output":102,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16864,"cost":{"input":-16762,"output":-102,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-16864}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774183022931}}
{"type":"message","id":"3aaedf61","parentId":"88a1a1f0","timestamp":"2026-03-22T12:39:53.892Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-22 20:36:54 GMT+8] Exec completed (tidy-blo, code 0) :: Registered feishu_im_bot_image tool [plugins] feishu_im: Registered feishu_im_bot_image [plugins] Registered all OAPI tools (calendar, task, bitable, search, drive, wiki, sheets, …\nSystem: [2026-03-22 20:39:53 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b54ca7f4490a8c3ea8929a42334b]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54ca7f4490a8c3ea8929a42334b\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-22 20:39 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n只安装这个就可以了吗， 不需要安装openclaw-memory了吗"}],"timestamp":1774183193889}}
{"type":"message","id":"2b4ffff4","parentId":"3aaedf61","timestamp":"2026-03-22T12:40:02.197Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Need to answer: only install memory-lancedb-pro is enough, no need openclaw-memory. Explain that memory-lancedb-pro provides functionality.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"只安装 **`memory‑lancedb‑pro`**（或 `openviking`）就能实现记忆增强，**不必额外再装 `openclaw-memory`**。  \n\n- `memory‑lancedb‑pro` 本身就是 OpenClaw 官方提供的记忆增强插件，内部已经实现了向量化存储、语义检索以及与 `memory_search` / `memory_get` 的完整兼容。  \n- `openclaw-memory` 是早期的通用记忆插件，而 `memory‑lancedb‑pro` 已经在它的基础上实现了更轻量的本地 LanceDB 后端，功能上完全覆盖（向量化、持久化、检索），并且更易部署。  \n\n**所以：**  \n1. 运行 `npx -y @openclaw/plugin-memory-lancedb-pro@latest install`（或 `openviking`）即可。  \n2. 安装完成后 **重启网关**：`openclaw gateway restart`。  \n3. 之后照常使用 `memory_search` / `memory_get`，插件会自动把写入的 `memory/*.md`、`MEMORY.md` 同步进向量库，无需再做其他配置。  \n\n如果以后想切换到其他向量后端（比如 Milvus、VikingDB），只需更改插件或配置，同样不需要同时保留 `openclaw-memory`。  \n\n因此，安装 `memory‑lancedb‑pro`（或你选的 `openviking`）即可满足记忆增强的需求。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":17222,"output":427,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17649,"cost":{"input":-17222,"output":-427,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-17649}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774183193891}}
